rows.label: qev300181_MSG0001
rows.name: Oh! Are you perhaps the deliverer of miranium?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300181_MSG0002
rows.name:
I requested 5,700 units, which I know is kind of an odd
number to ask for, even though it's an even number...
But, er, do you happen to have it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300181_SEL0021
rows.name: Hold on to your miranium for now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300181_MSG0004
rows.name:
Thank you. It's a bit of a mystery what I'm making
with all this, isn't it? I suppose you'll have to wait for
the big reveal, won't you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300181_MSG0005
rows.name: Was this just some of of your human teasing?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300181_MSG0006
rows.name:
I hope fate has pity on on your poor, miranium-lacking
self, okay?[ST:wait ]
